{
  "title": "Delicious Dutch Chicken Stew",
  "description": "A hearty and flavorful stew featuring chicken stock concentrate, perfect for a hangover cure or a comforting meal. This dish is known for its grassy and juicy flavors.",
  "cuisine": "Dutch",
  "diet": [
    "gluten-free",
